            <h1 class="heading-1">Why are We Building this System?</h1>
            <p class="para-1">
                I have worked in the social services field for fifteen years, and one issue I have encountered time and time again is the lack of ability for nonprofits to coordinate and communicate with each other regarding shared clientele.  This Community Case Management System will make it possible to share information regarding currently available resources.  It will give nonprofits the ability to send referrals directly to other nonprofits across the state.  Participating nonprofits will have a fully functional case management system similar to ones used by large government organizations. Finally, and most importantly nonprofits will have the ability, with written consent of the client, to share and read progress notes from partnering nonprofits in order to maximize the benefit to the client and eliminate wasted time and resources.  This application will revolutionize social service delivery.
            </p>

