                            <h4 class="card-title">Leveraging New Technology</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">In the second phase of the application build, after the initial role out.  We will be implementing Microsoft’s free and opensource Machine Learning Framework ML.NET in order to deliver the highest quality analytics that current technology can provide.  Machine learning is currently used to predict your next purchase, it is used to determine which social media post you see and what advertisements will be most effective.  We are going to use Machine Learning for positive social change. Intersectionality is real and can be incredibly complex, we will use Machine Learning to make predictions about what combination of services are most effective for various groups.  This will provide every participating organization with accurate feedback which they can use to make adjustments to their service delivery.  </p>
